OL,6,FSouth West Water (SWW) also revealed
OL,7,Fthat their underlying operating
OL,8,Fprofits increased by 8.6% to #166.3
OL,9,Fmillion in the year to 31 March 2024.
OL,11,FIt's despite the company being fined a
