OL,3,CWater company hikes dividend payout to
OL,4,Cshareholders amid parasite outbreak
OL,6,FGroup chief executive Susan Davy said:
OL,7,F"Whilst the results we are announcing
OL,8,Ftoday are based on our performance for
OL,9,Fthe last financial year, we are 100%
OL,10,Ffocused on returning a safe water
OL,11,Fsupply to the people and businesses in
OL,12,Fand around Brixham.
OL,14,F"Normal service has returned for 85%
OL,15,Fof customers but we won't stop until
OL,16,Fthe local drinking water is returned
OL,17,Fto the quality all our customers
OL,18,Fexpect and deserve.
