OL,6,F'A crisis of confidence in South West
OL,7,FWater'
OL,9,FSouth West Water has faced heavy
OL,10,Fcriticism in the last two weeks for
OL,11,Fit's handling of the situation in
OL,12,FBrixham.
OL,14,FSWW's parent company, Pennon, has
OL,15,Fincreased customer compensation to
OL,16,F#215 for those affected, adding that
OL,17,Fnormal service has now been restored
OL,18,Ffor 85% of customers. But this
OL,19,Ffollowed criticism of their initial
OL,20,Foffering of #15, which was quickly
OL,21,Fraised to #115.
