OL,6,FMPs from both Labour and the
OL,7,FConservatives have also warned the
OL,8,Fcompany will need to rebuild trust
OL,9,Fwith customers.
OL,11,F"There is a crisis of confidence in
OL,12,FSouth West Water," said Luke Pollard,
OL,13,Fthe Labour MP for Plymouth Sutton and
OL,14,FDevonport.
