OL,6,FHe added: "Their response has been
OL,7,Ffrankly hopeless, they've had poor
OL,8,Fcommunications, poor initial
OL,9,Fcompensation - in that every pound
OL,10,Fseems to have to be dragged out of
OL,11,Fthem - and they have a record of
OL,12,Ffailure on sewage."
OL,14,FSimon Jupp, the Conservative MP for
OL,15,FEast Devon, called for compensation
OL,16,Ffor those who had fallen ill, as well
OL,17,Fas for hospitality and tourism
OL,18,Fbusinesses across the county who "have
OL,19,Fseen their takings slashed and
OL,20,Fbookings cancelled."
